Sorry folks, code comments and seeds may be in Hungarian, send questions if any to miklos.beky@gmail.com

API can be found at http://hazaitop.addig.hu/front/api

A working Hungarian application is at: http://hazaitop.addig.hu/
In progress translation to English at: http://en.hazaitop.addig.hu/

If you are not familiar with Ruby on Rails, don't be afraid you can learn it fast:

ruby:
http://www.ruby-lang.org/en/documentation/quickstart/

rails:
http://guides.rubyonrails.org/v2.3.8/ for this project

hobo:
http://cookbook.hobocentral.net/tutorials/agility/

Visualization improvements are welcomed very much! :)

